    "data": [
        {
            "title": "警旺角截可疑私家車檢大量大麻油等毒品 男司機被捕",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/3a7e4305103968458ab449c6b4036a09/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250216/_2025021619084368510.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>旺角發現毒品快餐車。今日（16日）下午時份，警方於旺角一帶巡邏期間，於新填地街344號對開發現一輛黑色私家車形迹可疑，遂上前截查。警員在該輛私家車的司機位、乘客位及車尾位置發現大量毒品，包括大麻花、大麻草、大麻油、大麻糖及毒郵票等，約重4公斤。\n\n</p>\n<p><br/>\n警員遂以涉嫌「販運危險藥物」拘捕一名40多歲的本地男司機，他現正被扣留調查，行動中檢獲的毒品總市值仍在點算中。據了解，男子無業，有黑社會背景。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4084116/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"被捕男子無業，有黑社會背景。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/998411d204b80788b7ceb7bc93d0ce43/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250216_182939298_11.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        被捕男子無業，有黑社會背景。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4084117/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在車內發現大量毒品。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/663f0dece48a7cd82820a30a057e64ed/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250216_182939298_09.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在車內發現大量毒品。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4084118/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在車內發現大量毒品。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1785bb72f49066f1f080f5595e22ce60/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250216_182939298_08.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在車內發現大量毒品。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4084119/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在車內發現大量毒品。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/c368cd75e829655621334ef97b19baba/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250216_182939298_07.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在車內發現大量毒品。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4084120/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"警方在車內發現大量毒品。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7e25e8a5647a301429bb66c81da0dfc0/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250216_182939298_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        警方在車內發現大量毒品。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4084121/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"一輛黑色私家車停泊在新填地街344號對開，警方覺得形迹可疑，遂上前截查。尹敬堂攝\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2521cd8cb6ca2ddb485ab170246b2262/2025-02/KakaoTalk_20250216_182939298.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        一輛黑色私家車停泊在新填地街344號對開，警方覺得形迹可疑，遂上前截查。尹敬堂攝\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
